Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.21,0:00:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dreadful...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.75,0:00:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean that country in Asia?\NWhere they do that "harakiri"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pleased to meet you, Lord Horikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Kingdom of Albion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.83,0:00:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I am greatly honored that you would\Nwelcome us yourself, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.92,0:00:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It basically means our "princess of air"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is all they're willing to send\Nfor an Eastern island nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.21,0:00:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They've likely considered the risks involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.08,0:00:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt the Crown is unaware\Nof the assassination attempts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.21,0:00:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The assassins' ringleader is Todo Jubei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.67,0:00:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently he's single-handedly cut down 100 men.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.75,0:01:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,These undeveloped countries\Nand their overblown rumors...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in a European military report.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.71,0:01:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,During the Boshin War, he boarded\Nan ironclad ship and sank it unaided.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, now that\Nwe have the Princess on our side,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.13,0:01:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I would hate for her to get caught up\Nin an assassination plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.33,0:01:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.96,0:01:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what our Principal is for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.13,0:01:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had the royal car prepared for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.67,0:01:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It will take us to London. This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.21,0:01:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All this, for us. We are deeply in your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We entrust ourselves to your care on our journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:01:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,These Japanese people are peculiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:02:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they'd love to hear that\Nfrom a native of the Black Lizard Planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand you came here\Nto revise the treaty, Lord Horikawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The current terms are far too one-sided.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, this is a result of our own ignorance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:04:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Horikawa-sama, this is not the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see how important this is to you, Lord Horikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no authority over it myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can promise you a meeting with my Grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I am in your debt. Truly, truly in your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, you mustn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on a moving train. No one could...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You Western women have no manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When you ask someone's name, you first name yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Todo Jubei?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect you to be a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Two handguns.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,At your bosom and behind your waist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And your left shoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You have something hidden there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear the faint clinking of metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Jumping onto a train with no backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a legendary killer for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You little-!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Dorothy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is truly vast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,To think I would find such martial skill in the West.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You impress me, too. So the story\Nabout you killing 100 men was hardly fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She is not the assassin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold your fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She's NOT our enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.17,0:06:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Chise-dono, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You know why I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,To slay Todo Jubei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have come to this distant foreign land.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't send you back alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,For the time being, I will allow you\Nto accompany me as far as London.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.71,0:06:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, My Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:07:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You have my word, I will protect you\Nand put an end to those rebels.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We agreed to take you with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but any fighting will...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I know Todo Jubei better than any of your samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,With Princess onboard,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.04,0:07:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot allow any dubious characters to ride this train.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You question my intent?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You ARE a stowaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then allow me to prove my trustworthiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Chise-dono, put your sword away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to be Miss Chise's buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"Buddy," "buddy"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It means "partner."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? Partner to HER?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,this isn't funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.79,0:07:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If this girl is dangerous,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that's all the more reason to put her\Nunder the watchful eye of someone I can trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a platoon of 50 railroad security guards\Nriding in Car 5 and the caboose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It will take more than a flimsy attack to kill Lord Horikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.13,0:08:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Jubei's attacks are not flimsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you fought him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you fight him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it a matter of principle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Or was it some matter between the masters you serve?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this an interrogation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're buddies. We need to get to know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.92,0:08:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I hail from the Saga domain. A samurai clan. Age 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I like pickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ange. Age 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I come from the Black Lizard Planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! That's how you learned those martial arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Kaguya, too, came from the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It all makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You have Selenites in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only people from among the stars.\NWe live close to the gods, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Close to the gods?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They reside in the mountains, the rivers,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,even in the latrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only stop before we get to London.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is to say, if he were to attack, he would do it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take the pain away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Owie, owie,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.33,0:09:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,fly away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Owie, owie,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,fly away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.25,0:10:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Better?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,An Eastern magic spell\Nhanded down to me from my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He cast it for me many times in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are we helping Todo Jubei?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no interest in that eastern island nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I only hope he gets that woman\Ncaught up in an assassination plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She may be only a figurehead,\Nbut she's fourth in line to the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't be sure someone won't move her ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So he didn't come after us at Maidstone Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the fearsome Jubei is out of his element\Nin a foreign nation, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He will appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Jubei isn't such a simple opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so obsessed with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.46,0:11:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Jubei...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,killed my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Two years ago, time stopped for me completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And until I strike Jubei down,\Nmy tears refuse to be shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And what do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was watching the janitor, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Todo Jubei?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,An explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.88,0:12:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go see what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The outbound trains should all have\Nstopped running for security reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.38,0:12:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo Jubei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see the Duke of Normandy kept his promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Slow down the engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to get back to the soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't! If we slow down while we're\Nstill connected, we'll derail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's boarding the train!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, draw your swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.71,0:13:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.38,0:13:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dorothy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In the state car. Go to her, Ange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,With your C-ball, you can still catch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That is where we'll find Jubei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.33,0:14:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take all the help I can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow my timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.83,0:14:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You would betray us, Chise-dono?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the traitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:14:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you-!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,SHE is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Go faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fall behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll drag us off the rails!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.96,0:15:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The tracks merge up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If the cars hit each other at this speed,\Nit will be a catastrophe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ange!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.21,0:15:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them board!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They went up top!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Such incredible skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Jubei-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oshima?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.75,0:16:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Horikawa. I am here for your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.67,0:16:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic remnant of the Shogunate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect our lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness, get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Beatrice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Some sort of armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,JUBEI!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.92,0:16:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ange!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stop these trains!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.04,0:17:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Close the regulator valve!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the red lever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn the reversing gear to the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, open the bypass valve!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.33,0:18:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And brake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.29,0:18:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You've grown stronger, Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Chise, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be at ease, Lord Horikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I have slain the traitor, Todo Jubei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.25,0:19:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Jubei was your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The caring father who taught me the sword was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.13,0:19:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The man resting here is nothing more\Nthan a traitorous assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.29,0:20:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.04,0:20:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no need for your sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather, I am proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.38,0:20:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to surpass my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. Dorothy is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Chise...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.29,0:20:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for keeping Princess safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Owie, owie, fly away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.54,0:20:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Owie, owie, fly away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.83,0:20:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,0:20:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Your spell isn't working, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:20:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't take away the pain in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.67,0:21:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Should you really be drinking alcohol?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry. My wounds have closed up nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna see?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're-!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A new transfer student. Todo Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Transfer student?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We're glad to have you, Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This room is our base of operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it lovely?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.25,0:21:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.04,0:21:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Our respective employers have struck a deal.\NI will be helping with Operation: Changeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I introduced Lord Horikawa to Control.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.29,0:21:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he might switch over to the Commonwealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:21:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you s-s-seduce Lord Horikawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You nobles use such naughty language.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But wh-what else could I call it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.13,0:22:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ange. You made it possible for me to fight Jubei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.04,0:22:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to thank you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.29,0:22:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.29,0:22:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to live in our country,\NI'll teach you how we do it in the West.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.71,0:22:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called a handshake.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.54,0:22:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,These Western customs aren't so bad.
